\frac {d}{dx}(\cos x\sin^{n-1}x)=-\sin^n x+(n-1)\cos^2x\sin^{n-2}x
= -\sin^n x+(n-1)(1-\sin^2x)\sin^{n-2}x=-n\sin^nx+(n-1)sin^{n-2}x
\cos x\sin^{n-1}x=0
0=-nI_n+(n-1)I_{n-2}
I_n=\frac {(n-1)}nI_{n-2}
